summary: Are you sure BC isn't anorexic? Being around Zero and her nasty cohorts would put anyone off their feed for awhile, but this is...
question: Are you sure BC isn't anorexic? Being around Zero and her nasty cohorts would put anyone off their feed for awhile, but this is getting ridiculous!
answer: Sigh. I’m not saying he is or he isn’t…I just think SOMETHING is wrong….very wrong. It could be any number of things. I know that when I get super stressed, it affects my ability to maintain my weight and I have to take meds to settle my stomach and be able to keep food down. And if he’s trying to remain Vegan during all of this? That could be a factor, too. But someone really needs to get him to a doctor, because whatever he’s doing right now is not working.
